Author: tseokii
Text: I feel like I wrote this. I'm not friends with her anymore but I had one friend do this to me constantly. I was always trying to figure out if it was intentional (like a bragging thing?) or not. But I don't think it was, she did the same thing where she'd eat a really small amount of food once or twice but forget about it.  Buhhhhh I hate it. Even if it's not true that they haven't eaten. Even if I'm skinnier than them. If I've eaten more than them that day when they say it, I just feel like shit. I'm stupid lol
